body:
Removing the Python 2 only branches works. According to the docs SWIG [should not mess with C preprocessor stuff](http://www.swig.org/Doc3.0/SWIGDocumentation.html#SWIG_nn6), but it seems that's wrong :)

I think `%{ }` only works for things to be included in the interface header, isn't it?
